==============================================================================
BUG2 Algorithm Implementation
==============================================================================

BUG2 is a local path palnning algoritm with a global goal.

BUG2 Algorithm:

* Head towards goal on the m-line.
* if any obstacle is found, follow it untill you raech m-line again (closer to goal).
*continue on the m-line. 

The Visualization can be seen using rviz

launch:

roslaunch bug2_ros bug2.launch

==============================================================================
 
BUG Algorithms in detail:

https://www.cs.cmu.edu/~motionplanning/lecture/Chap2-Bug-Alg_howie.pdf

==============================================================================
